item.title: Apex-OS looking for experienced developers
item.dc:creator: @my-swagger my-swagger
item.description:
@my-swagger wrote:

[quote=“Zach Knight, post:4, topic:553568”][quote author=Justin Bieber link=topic=672481.msg4497340#msg4497340 date=1445094682]

I got excited when I seen the name ended with OS and thought you were devving an operating system then got really really disappointed when I seen it was a 317 RSPS with such a name. Very misleading project name.
[/quote]too bad u don’t even know how to make an os rofl

Depends on what you classify as making an OS. Many would consider putting a Linux distribution together making an OS, and I’d agree, and that is incredibly easy to do.[/quote]
Depends on what you mean by that, using the Linux kernal is really cool. Making your own? Life will not be worth it.
